{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of badge","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"badge","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSBadge"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBadgeComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BadgeComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"badge","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Badge","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of dimensions ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProviders"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider\/init(spaces:dimensions:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","generated":true},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider\/dimensions","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties","generated":true},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider\/BadgeComponentTokens-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations"],"anchor":"Default-Implementations","title":"Default Implementations","generated":true}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for badge component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomBadgeComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the badge component tokens you want.","","        override var sizeXsmall: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._100 }","","        override var spaceInset: SpaceSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens.outOfSystem75 }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomBadgeComponentTokensProvider: BadgeComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomBadgeComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(badge: CustomBadgeComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    OrangeTheme(badge: CustomBadgeComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    let badgeComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own dimension and space semantic tokens provider","    let badgeComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider(","                    spaces: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider(),","                    dimensions: CustomDimensionSemanticTokensProvider())"]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.10.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","name":"Since","style":"note"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider"},"relationshipsSections":